	(text "Atmega Hardware Design Considerations p7,p8 -> 10kR, 100nF cap and 330R for switch. The 100nF is not used in Arduino (produces erors with DTR)\nThe 100nF capacitor on DTR (CH340C) is used for tricking Arduino into Bootloader mode, it produces a voltage spike.\n\n"
