	(text "AMS1117 p4 -> 22uF tantalum capacitor on output\nLMS1117 p16-> 10uF tantalum capacitor the input. I will use a 22uF to reuse the same capacitor\nI will reuse the output capacitor of AMS1117-5V to be the output capacitor of AMS1117-3.3V"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 29.21 175.26 0)
